messages:
Name: Sebastian Szymanski
Nationality: Poland
Date of Birth: May 10, 1999
Position: Midfielder
Current club: Feyenoord
Eredivisie clubs played for: Feyenoord

Feyenoord's Sebastian Szymanski has taken part in the vast majority of the side's Eredivisie games in 2022/2023, making 29 appearances overall and playing 1,974 minutes. He has started in 24 of these appearances across their 34 fixtures and entered as a substitute on five occasions.

Szymanski last made an appearance in a league game on May 28, playing 90 minutes for Feyenoord against Vitesse in a 1-0 loss. The midfielder has scored nine Eredivisie goals this season. He has amassed three yellow cards.

Szymanski was last on target in the league in the 3-1 win against Utrecht on April 23, netting in the 15th minute. He opened his account for the campaign against Emmen on August 27, scoring during a 4-0 victory.
Szymanski played 27 Premier League games last season for Dinamo Moskva, scored six goals and provided eight assists.
Szymanski switched to Feyenoord on loan in July 2022 from Dinamo Moskva, for whom he has made 143 league appearances in total, scoring 15 goals and providing 26 assists.
